  <entry>
    <title>「MMD 靜畫」偷笑</title>
    <link href="https://copy-alcide.github.io/MMDPic/2022/MMDPic-20220730/"/>
    <id>https://copy-alcide.github.io/MMDPic/2022/MMDPic-20220730/</id>
    <published>2022-07-30T08:03:40.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-07-30T08:47:15.346Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/copy-alcide/CopyBlogImage@main//Hatate_20220730.png"></p><p>之前在群聊裏看到砌磚裏面新出場的果果，超級可愛。嘗試模仿其中一張做了這個。</p><p>這次調整光照調整了好久，最終結果感覺還行……？</p><span id="more"></span><figure class="highlight plaintext"><figcaption><span>Text</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">借物表</span><br><span class="line">模型：</span><br><span class="line">歌奈斗 MikuMikuDance用　東方Project 「姫海棠はたて」モデルデータ</span><br><span class="line">歌奈斗 ケータイ</span><br><span class="line">鯖缶 人里</span><br><span class="line">渲染：</span><br><span class="line">Ray-MMD by Rui</span><br><span class="line">dPostPointLight_v1.00 by 極北P</span><br><span class="line">面光源エフェクト PanelLight by そぼろ</span><br><span class="line">不透明水彩風にするエフェクト by ikeno</span><br><span class="line"> 発光エフェクト AutoLuminous by そぼろ</span><br><span class="line">Toon_RC by RedialC</span><br><span class="line">RayMMD用のマテリアル24種類 by 世界最弱のサーモントラウト</span><br><span class="line">軟件：</span><br><span class="line">MMM ver 1.2.9.2</span><br><span class="line">MMD ver 9.26</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/copy-alcide/CopyBlogImage@main//Hatate_20220730.png&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;之前在群聊裏看到砌磚裏面新出場的果果，超級可愛。嘗試模仿其中一張做了這個。&lt;/p&gt;
